membership:
EUROCOTON is a member of or participates in meetings of:&#xd;
- EURATEX, "The European Apparel and Textile Confederation", Belgium;&#xd;
- GAFTT, the "Global Alliance for Fair Textile Trade", Washington (US), however inactive for several years;&#xd;
- BUSINESSEUROPE, only the open sessions of the International Relations Committee, Belgium;&#xd;
- some sectors' alliances (Origin Marking, ...);&#xd;
- ITMF "International Textile Manufacturers Federation", Switzerland.

memberOrga:
Members of EUROCOTON (Full, Associate and Corporate members):&#xd;
- Fédération Française des Industries Lainière et Cotonnière (FFILC), France;&#xd;
- Fédération de l'industrie belge du textile, du bois et de l'ameublement (Fedustria), Belgium;&#xd;
- Industrieverband Veredlung, Garne, Gewebe, Technische Textilien e.V. (IVGT), Germany;&#xd;
- Federation of Greek Textile Industrialists, Greece;&#xd;
- Gdynia Cotton Association, Poland;&#xd;
- Hellenic Cotton Association of Ginners and Exporters, Greece;&#xd;
- Agrupacion Espanola de Desmotadores de Algodon (AEDA), Spain;&#xd;
- Lenzing AG, Austria;&#xd;
- Klopman International S.r.l., Italy.
